(41, 8, 22, 42, 10, 13, 13, 'Bethsaida', 'Connection Between Bethsaida References', 'Both passages emphasize Bethsaida, highlighting its significance in Jesus'' ministry. The mention of mighty works in Bethsaida in Luke underscores the importance of the healing in Mark.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
